WEBVTT

01:50.800 --> 01:53.760
It's already dawn,
and we've heard all the stories.

01:53.840 --> 01:55.240
Why aren't they out yet?

01:58.440 --> 01:59.760
They're driving me crazy.

02:01.120 --> 02:02.160
In fact,

02:03.600 --> 02:05.640
there is one other way to help Mu Long.

02:07.240 --> 02:08.320
Say it.

02:11.880 --> 02:13.120
The solution lies inside you.

02:15.080 --> 02:18.080
You mean the Dragon Deity's Power?

02:34.880 --> 02:36.120
That scent…

02:38.240 --> 02:39.400
Master Dragon Deity?

02:43.560 --> 02:45.440
Searing flames, ignite!

03:36.800 --> 03:38.120
You're not Lu Wuyi.

03:56.840 --> 03:57.960
Come with me.

03:58.480 --> 03:59.560
Master Dragon Deity?

04:02.080 --> 04:03.040
It's you?

04:07.080 --> 04:08.920
So you really are helping Lu Wuyi.

04:10.240 --> 04:11.360
Wuyi,

04:13.280 --> 04:14.320
what happened to you?

04:15.360 --> 04:16.320
-Wu…
-It was him.

04:17.920 --> 04:19.800
He used Word Magic on Mu Long.

04:21.079 --> 04:22.840
He joined forces with Jiu Ying long ago.

04:23.840 --> 04:25.040
I found out,

04:25.920 --> 04:27.760
and when I tried to tell you, Wangyan,

04:28.800 --> 04:30.240
he wounded me.

04:32.680 --> 04:35.120
Ji Ling hurt you?

04:39.280 --> 04:42.000
<i>Ji, help me.</i>

04:42.560 --> 04:44.320
<i>I'm afraid that if Wangyan</i>
<i>learns the truth,</i>

04:45.400 --> 04:46.600
<i>she'll come to despise me.</i>

04:47.400 --> 04:49.000
<i>I don't want to lose her.</i>

05:01.240 --> 05:02.720
You're not saying anything.

05:02.800 --> 05:03.840
Are you admitting it?

05:08.800 --> 05:10.040
Why did you give me this bracelet?

05:12.720 --> 05:15.920
Bai Ze's Eastern Purple Lightning
can suppress evil.

05:18.240 --> 05:21.720
Wear it, and it can temporarily suppress
Jiu Ying's spirit fragment.

05:26.920 --> 05:29.360
Is it really meant to suppress
Jiu Ying's spirit fragment?

05:29.440 --> 05:30.560
That bracelet is fake.

05:33.200 --> 05:36.960
Ji Ling, didn't you say that bracelet
could suppress Jiu Ying's fragment?

05:37.560 --> 05:38.520
Was it a lie?

05:40.560 --> 05:42.040
If I hadn't lied to him,

05:42.680 --> 05:44.800
how could I have lowered his guard?

05:46.480 --> 05:48.200
You can go kill Chi Wen now.

05:48.920 --> 05:50.720
You really did keep your promise.

05:51.840 --> 05:53.400
Now you can sit

05:54.000 --> 05:55.880
on the Dragon Deity's throne

05:56.920 --> 05:58.000
<i>forever.</i>

06:05.320 --> 06:06.240
I believe Wuyi.

06:08.240 --> 06:09.400
Wangyan…

06:09.480 --> 06:11.560
You've sat on the Dragon Deity's throne
too long.

06:11.640 --> 06:13.880
You don't want to give it up, do you?

06:13.960 --> 06:15.760
As long as the Word Magic
on Mu Long isn't lifted,

06:16.480 --> 06:18.520
Han Ba won't hand over
the Dragon Deity's Power,

06:20.000 --> 06:22.120
and Wu Shiguang
won't be able to become a dragon.

06:22.200 --> 06:25.560
And that means the throne stays his.

06:26.160 --> 06:28.560
You betrayed your oath to Master Chi Wen.

06:28.640 --> 06:32.760
Didn't you reclaim your demon power too,
betraying your oath just the same?

06:33.520 --> 06:35.280
You have no right to accuse me.

06:37.080 --> 06:39.040
But why did he snatch Mu Long's pendant?

06:39.120 --> 06:41.520
Because Su Jian's memories
are stored inside it.

06:41.600 --> 06:45.400
He wanted to help Jiu Ying
hide something shameful.

06:47.080 --> 06:48.680
It has Jian's memories inside.

06:56.080 --> 06:57.760
Even if you take the pendant,
it won't help.

06:57.840 --> 06:58.720
We already know everything.

06:59.600 --> 07:03.720
Lu Wuyi was created by Jiu Ying,

07:04.480 --> 07:05.520
wasn't she?

07:21.520 --> 07:22.680
It's empty?

07:23.320 --> 07:24.480
The memories are gone.

07:29.240 --> 07:30.680
You lied to me.

07:38.600 --> 07:39.640
So she took

07:41.920 --> 07:43.600
the memories back.

07:44.720 --> 07:45.560
The manuscript!

07:45.640 --> 07:48.600
The first chapter of that manuscript
was Little Pomegranate's story.

07:48.680 --> 07:50.720
The handwriting was all crooked.

07:50.800 --> 07:52.520
It was really ugly.

07:52.600 --> 07:54.440
<i>But still, I recognized the words</i>
<i>"Little" and "Pomegranate".</i>

07:54.520 --> 07:55.360
THE GREAT DEMON AND LITTLE POMEGRANATE

07:55.440 --> 07:57.000
That was Su Jian's handwriting.

07:57.640 --> 07:59.160
She wrote the story

08:01.520 --> 08:02.680
of Little Pomegranate.

08:12.600 --> 08:15.400
Master Dragon Deity returned this to us.

08:15.480 --> 08:17.040
<i>He didn't want it.</i>

08:28.040 --> 08:29.560
I'll go bring the medicine over.

10:05.920 --> 10:10.360
NIAN

10:35.360 --> 10:36.640
<i>So what she wrote was "Nian",</i>

10:38.760 --> 10:40.600
as in never forgetting.

10:47.280 --> 10:48.920
So whenever the wind stirred the tree,

10:50.400 --> 10:51.880
<i>all it carried</i>

10:53.160 --> 10:54.440
<i>were sighs.</i>

10:56.720 --> 10:59.000
And yet I never had the courage
to go up to her.

11:14.000 --> 11:15.600
Don't go. It's dangerous.

11:24.360 --> 11:25.800
His demon power is leaking out.

11:27.080 --> 11:29.680
<i>To keep another drought from breaking out,</i>

11:29.760 --> 11:31.800
<i>I grant you the Dragon Deity's Power.</i>

11:31.880 --> 11:34.720
<i>It can temporarily stop</i>
<i>your demonic energy from leaking.</i>

11:35.720 --> 11:38.960
<i>But this borrowed power</i>
<i>will run out one day.</i>

11:39.040 --> 11:41.840
Wangyan, Han Ba's mind is in chaos.

11:42.440 --> 11:44.240
He's about to lose control
of his demon power.

11:47.440 --> 11:48.600
I won't be able

11:49.200 --> 11:52.400
to see Mu Long finish
her story collection after all.

11:56.360 --> 11:57.960
I hid the Dragon Deity's Power

11:59.520 --> 12:01.520
in the place where I first met Su Jian.

12:03.800 --> 12:05.360
I placed a seal on it.

12:06.040 --> 12:08.160
Only when Mu Long regains consciousness

12:08.240 --> 12:10.080
will it be unsealed.

12:11.880 --> 12:13.360
Please, save Mu Long for me.

12:17.920 --> 12:20.000
I'm sorry that even at the very end,

12:20.680 --> 12:22.560
I'm still this selfish.

12:33.120 --> 12:34.240
<i>This is for you.</i>

12:34.320 --> 12:37.880
<i>At just over 20, you're the perfect age</i>
<i>for carrying an old man's fan.</i>

13:22.480 --> 13:23.640
I'm coming…

13:25.640 --> 13:27.040
to you.

14:10.800 --> 14:12.760
Because of what you did,

14:12.840 --> 14:14.800
none of this can be undone now.

14:15.560 --> 14:17.320
The memories were long gone
from that pendant.

14:17.400 --> 14:19.480
Whether I took it or not,

14:19.560 --> 14:20.800
nothing could have prevented

14:20.880 --> 14:22.920
Han Ba's collapse
after learning the truth.

14:23.800 --> 14:24.920
The ending was written from the start.

14:25.600 --> 14:27.080
Blaming me won't change a thing.

14:28.680 --> 14:30.040
Such is fate.

14:31.800 --> 14:33.360
No matter how many times we try,

14:37.800 --> 14:39.200
some things can never be undone.

14:41.760 --> 14:44.920
Some people are destined
to be like two great mountains

14:46.000 --> 14:49.520
separated by an endless plain, a canyon,

14:50.320 --> 14:52.680
or a distance they can never cross.

14:53.280 --> 14:54.880
They watch over each other from afar,

14:56.040 --> 14:58.440
yet can never take one step
or even half a step

15:00.360 --> 15:01.520
toward one another.

15:02.880 --> 15:03.880
Tell me.

15:05.360 --> 15:06.480
Tell me.

15:08.400 --> 15:09.880
What are they waiting for?

15:11.120 --> 15:12.720
What are they waiting for?

15:14.840 --> 15:16.160
They're waiting for a snowfall.

15:17.760 --> 15:19.160
They're waiting for a snowfall.

15:21.240 --> 15:22.600
With just one snowfall,

15:23.320 --> 15:26.960
they can bow to each other from afar
and grow old together.

15:27.760 --> 15:29.120
With just one snowfall,

15:30.120 --> 15:32.360
they can bow to each other from afar

15:33.000 --> 15:34.440
and grow old together.

15:47.200 --> 15:49.040
<i>What, you don't like it anymore?</i>

15:51.080 --> 15:53.160
It doesn't really go
with what I'm wearing today.

15:59.520 --> 16:00.560
Come with me!

16:03.760 --> 16:05.000
Wuyi!

16:11.720 --> 16:14.400
I wonder whether Wu Shiguang and Wangyan

16:14.480 --> 16:16.280
will be able to find Ji Ling and Wuyi.

16:17.400 --> 16:19.640
Right now, only Ji Ling can wake you.

16:20.400 --> 16:21.840
There's nothing I can do to help.

16:41.000 --> 16:43.120
Su Jian treated me like her older sister,

16:43.200 --> 16:44.600
yet I forgot her.

16:46.360 --> 16:48.760
Ji Ling took Wuyi away
right in front of me,

16:49.560 --> 16:51.240
yet there was nothing I could do.

16:53.880 --> 16:56.920
Do you still think of her
as your little sister?

16:57.000 --> 16:58.960
She is my little sister.

17:02.920 --> 17:05.640
Maybe I can't tell
real memories from fake ones,

17:07.880 --> 17:09.880
but when Jiu Ying held me captive,

17:09.960 --> 17:11.119
<i>it was Lu Wuyi</i>

17:11.200 --> 17:13.520
<i>-who risked everything to save me.</i>
-Wangyan…

17:14.560 --> 17:16.240
When she looked at me,

17:16.960 --> 17:19.680
<i>the trust and dependence in her eyes</i>

17:21.359 --> 17:22.599
couldn't have been fake.

17:23.680 --> 17:26.400
The one truly at fault in all this
is Ji Ling.

17:27.119 --> 17:28.920
Wuyi was blinded by love.

17:29.000 --> 17:30.880
That's why she covered for him.

17:33.720 --> 17:34.680
You lied to me.

17:45.080 --> 17:48.240
Whatever the truth is,
we have to find them first,

17:50.480 --> 17:51.760
not only to save Lu Wuyi,

17:52.400 --> 17:54.320
but also to put an end to this drought.

17:55.280 --> 17:57.880
I already have three strands
of the Dragon Deity's Power in me.

17:57.960 --> 18:00.720
Once I get the last one, I can transform
into a dragon and bring rain.

18:07.880 --> 18:09.360
I'll take you to Ji Ling.

18:10.600 --> 18:11.880
I know where he is.

18:14.520 --> 18:15.560
Why?

18:19.600 --> 18:21.360
Because I don't trust Lu Wuyi.

18:45.120 --> 18:46.160
Wu.

18:52.400 --> 18:54.360
Has the blowback
from the rewinds gotten worse?

18:56.040 --> 18:57.200
That's none of your concern.

19:08.280 --> 19:11.240
Wu, we are alone now.

19:12.640 --> 19:15.400
Tell me. Why did you lie to me?

19:20.040 --> 19:22.360
Since you've lived
through countless rewinds,

19:23.240 --> 19:24.720
you must've known
Wu Shiguang and the others

19:24.800 --> 19:26.760
learned the truth from the painting

19:28.240 --> 19:30.200
and that the pendant
was no longer important.

19:31.360 --> 19:32.600
And you must've known long ago

19:33.320 --> 19:35.200
that there were no memories
left inside it.

19:37.320 --> 19:38.480
Am I right?

19:39.280 --> 19:40.160
Yes.

19:49.440 --> 19:50.320
So,

19:52.560 --> 19:54.160
from the very beginning,

19:54.880 --> 19:57.480
this was a trap you carefully laid for me.

19:59.520 --> 20:01.960
Then why did you trick me into stealing

20:03.320 --> 20:04.600
that pendant for you?

20:09.840 --> 20:12.120
Because you killed my sister.

20:26.400 --> 20:27.720
I killed Wu Wangyan?

20:32.320 --> 20:34.000
Do you know

20:35.760 --> 20:37.160
who matters most to me

20:38.800 --> 20:39.720
in this world?

20:47.880 --> 20:48.920
Wu Wangyan.

20:54.120 --> 20:54.960
That's right.

20:56.840 --> 20:59.640
Even after she learned
that I was a monster created by Jiu Ying,

21:00.920 --> 21:04.720
that all my memories with her
were fabricated,

21:08.400 --> 21:09.600
she still saw me

21:12.320 --> 21:14.720
as her irreplaceable little sister.

21:24.600 --> 21:25.720
Wuyi,

21:27.640 --> 21:29.360
don't call yourself a monster.

21:30.640 --> 21:33.080
Don't call yourself trash
that nobody wants.

21:36.480 --> 21:39.240
I don't know what others can give you.

21:40.000 --> 21:43.440
But what I give you is my heart.

21:44.480 --> 21:47.000
You will always be
my most beloved little sister.

21:51.640 --> 21:55.400
Those words were meant for Su Jian,

21:55.480 --> 21:57.120
not for me.

21:57.800 --> 21:58.840
This isn't real.

22:03.240 --> 22:04.760
Then what about this?

22:06.800 --> 22:08.080
Is this fake too?

22:09.480 --> 22:10.640
Listen to me carefully.

22:11.240 --> 22:14.120
I will say this to you once again.

22:15.840 --> 22:17.640
I will always be by your side.

22:43.360 --> 22:44.680
You ruined her promise.

22:45.760 --> 22:46.880
You killed her.

22:47.600 --> 22:49.120
In all the previous rewinds,

22:51.160 --> 22:52.840
you killed her right in front of me.

22:54.960 --> 22:56.640
FIRST TIME

23:03.480 --> 23:05.360
You joined forces with Jiu Ying.

23:06.120 --> 23:09.960
You killed Wangyan
so Wu Shiguang would break down,

23:10.040 --> 23:13.600
giving Jiu Ying the chance
to seize Wu Shiguang's body.

23:14.480 --> 23:16.040
You said I lied to you.

23:16.960 --> 23:17.880
You're right.

23:20.800 --> 23:22.160
I did lie to you.

23:23.040 --> 23:25.120
I was never trapped in the time rewinds.

23:25.920 --> 23:28.600
I chose to start over again and again,

23:29.920 --> 23:31.280
so I could stop you.

23:32.920 --> 23:35.840
<i>Too bad I failed every time.</i>

23:36.520 --> 23:37.560
Wangyan!

23:41.440 --> 23:43.280
SECOND REWIND

23:43.360 --> 23:44.440
Wangyan!

23:55.600 --> 23:56.480
THIRD REWIND

23:56.560 --> 23:58.600
-Wangyan! What's wrong?
-Wuyi.

23:58.680 --> 24:00.080
Wangyan, listen to me.

24:00.160 --> 24:01.960
Ji Ling is going to kill you.
Come with me, now!

24:02.040 --> 24:03.440
Wuyi, what are you talking about?

24:03.520 --> 24:04.960
-I'm serious.
-Nobody…

24:05.040 --> 24:06.200
Wang…

24:06.280 --> 24:07.160
<i>Every single time,</i>

24:07.760 --> 24:09.200
<i>I had to watch my sister…</i>

24:09.280 --> 24:10.120
Wangyan.

24:10.200 --> 24:11.160
<i>…die by your hand.</i>

24:12.200 --> 24:13.040
FIFTH REWIND

24:13.120 --> 24:15.160
Wangyan! Wangyan!

24:17.800 --> 24:19.240
SIXTH REWIND

24:19.320 --> 24:20.360
Wangyan.

24:21.120 --> 24:25.480
SEVENTH REWIND

24:28.440 --> 24:30.920
EIGHTH REWIND

24:31.000 --> 24:34.080
NINTH REWIND

24:34.160 --> 24:35.960
TENTH REWIND

24:36.040 --> 24:37.680
ELEVENTH REWIND

24:37.760 --> 24:41.280
TWELFTH REWIND

24:41.360 --> 24:42.280
THIRTEENTH REWIND

24:42.360 --> 24:43.400
Ji Ling…

24:44.880 --> 24:46.920
You killed my sister.

24:47.000 --> 24:48.040
FIFTEENTH REWIND

24:48.120 --> 24:49.800
I'll never forgive you.

24:50.520 --> 24:52.480
SIXTEENTH REWIND

24:53.160 --> 24:54.360
I hate you.

24:54.440 --> 24:55.760
SEVENTEENTH REWIND

24:55.840 --> 24:57.480
I hate you!

25:05.080 --> 25:07.120
NINETEENTH REWIND

25:13.160 --> 25:16.040
<i>Again and again, I had to endure</i>
<i>that piercing, bone-deep pain,</i>

25:16.560 --> 25:18.080
<i>and still I couldn't change a thing.</i>

25:20.960 --> 25:22.000
But this time,

25:23.800 --> 25:24.640
I did it.

25:25.920 --> 25:28.680
Wu Shiguang didn't get
the Dragon Deity's Power kept by Han Ba,

25:28.760 --> 25:30.440
and Wangyan learned what you were after.

25:31.360 --> 25:33.360
Everyone has seen your true colors.

25:38.560 --> 25:39.600
Wu,

25:41.560 --> 25:44.400
do you know why I trusted you so much?

25:45.600 --> 25:49.160
Do you know why I was willing
to do everything you said?

25:53.200 --> 25:54.280
No.

25:56.040 --> 25:58.040
-Because…
-I don't want to know.

26:08.400 --> 26:09.440
So Wu Wangyan

26:13.360 --> 26:15.080
is the only one you truly care about.

26:19.160 --> 26:20.440
Because she

26:22.360 --> 26:23.520
truly cares about me too.

26:23.600 --> 26:25.120
Don't I care about you?

26:38.400 --> 26:39.600
No matter.

26:40.840 --> 26:42.080
I've grown used to it by now.

26:42.840 --> 26:46.440
The people around me always end up

26:47.040 --> 26:50.440
leaving me one by one.

26:52.680 --> 26:53.720
No one ever stays.

26:55.760 --> 26:57.600
Lift the Word Magic from Mu Long.

27:00.400 --> 27:01.520
Even if I die,

27:04.040 --> 27:05.920
I won't undo the Word Magic for you

27:06.720 --> 27:08.520
to let you get the Dragon Deity's Power.

28:19.040 --> 28:20.000
You knew I was here?

28:21.720 --> 28:25.320
Have you forgotten
how I found you in the first place?

28:26.160 --> 28:28.520
<i>Why did you appear</i>
<i>outside the Shilin Sect?</i>

28:28.600 --> 28:30.000
I don't know.

28:30.600 --> 28:34.080
I just felt a voice calling me,

28:35.000 --> 28:36.320
telling me to come here.

28:37.080 --> 28:38.640
All these years later,

28:39.880 --> 28:41.720
that obsession is still in me,

28:44.120 --> 28:45.240
telling me to go find you.

28:46.880 --> 28:48.280
And somehow, I always do.

28:49.800 --> 28:51.320
I wonder if I'll ever be able

28:53.400 --> 28:55.800
to figure out
where that obsession comes from.

28:56.640 --> 28:57.560
Li Jie,

28:58.800 --> 29:00.000
do you blame me

29:01.080 --> 29:02.720
for lying even to you?

29:07.760 --> 29:11.120
Though I don't know your true intentions,

29:11.200 --> 29:16.160
I have always known
what kind of person you are.

29:17.200 --> 29:20.200
In all the years I've stayed by your side,

29:20.880 --> 29:22.080
a lot of the time,

29:22.160 --> 29:25.880
I didn't understand
your choices or intentions.

29:26.960 --> 29:28.040
But I knew

29:30.280 --> 29:32.080
you must've had reasons
you couldn't speak of.

29:33.480 --> 29:37.640
I will always be
your shield and your blade.

29:40.000 --> 29:41.680
What do we do now?

29:43.760 --> 29:46.200
They're now all wary of me.

29:47.400 --> 29:49.560
Bring Mu Long here for me.

29:49.640 --> 29:53.160
I'll find a way to make Lu Wuyi
lift the Word Magic.

29:55.920 --> 29:56.760
Understood.

29:58.960 --> 30:00.120
Be careful.

30:24.160 --> 30:25.520
Give me back my sister!

30:37.920 --> 30:40.160
You're using the Dragon Deity's Power
against me?

30:40.760 --> 30:41.880
I'll go rescue Wuyi.

30:49.400 --> 30:50.760
You're trying to take my ring?

30:51.400 --> 30:53.120
I'm going to use Xiaowei's power
inside that ring

30:53.200 --> 30:55.240
to lift the Word Magic on Mu Long.

30:56.120 --> 30:58.240
Like the Twelve Thoughts,
the Spirit-Binding Ring

30:58.320 --> 30:59.240
obeys only its master.

31:00.560 --> 31:01.480
Even if you take it, it won't obey you.

31:02.720 --> 31:03.760
Its master?

31:04.480 --> 31:07.240
The ring's true master
is Chi Wen, not you.

31:08.320 --> 31:11.080
The Dragon Deity's Power in me
came from my brother.

31:11.920 --> 31:16.320
I'd like to see if it'll obey you over me!

31:23.480 --> 31:24.400
Ji Ling…

31:38.920 --> 31:40.120
Wangyan.

32:24.840 --> 32:25.880
Do you still

32:29.000 --> 32:30.640
see me as your little sister?

32:42.040 --> 32:43.320
No matter what happens,

32:45.600 --> 32:48.040
you will always be
my most beloved little sister.

32:49.760 --> 32:51.000
I will

32:53.280 --> 32:55.480
always be by your side.

33:01.240 --> 33:03.080
The Word Magic was cast by Lu Wuyi.

33:03.720 --> 33:05.440
Even if you take the ring, it won't help.

33:05.520 --> 33:06.760
Don't believe him!

33:10.360 --> 33:12.360
Wangyan's Word Magic
is far stronger than mine.

33:12.440 --> 33:14.240
If I had really cast it,

33:14.320 --> 33:16.000
how could she possibly fail to undo it?

33:16.520 --> 33:17.720
Wu Shiguang,

33:18.320 --> 33:20.800
Lu Wuyi somehow gained
the power to rewind time.

33:21.400 --> 33:24.200
Her power has already
surpassed all of ours.

33:24.920 --> 33:26.000
You're sharp enough.

33:26.880 --> 33:28.800
Haven't you noticed
anything strange about her?

33:36.120 --> 33:38.320
I don't know
which of you is telling the truth.

33:38.920 --> 33:39.920
But it doesn't matter.

33:40.000 --> 33:42.000
Once I get the Spirit-Binding Ring,

33:42.080 --> 33:43.480
I'll know.

34:00.640 --> 34:01.480
Wangyan,

34:08.280 --> 34:09.400
let's go.

34:57.120 --> 34:58.280
Master Dragon Deity…

35:02.000 --> 35:02.960
You Chi!

35:09.560 --> 35:10.800
Hand over the ring,

35:11.400 --> 35:12.600
or I'll kill him.

35:21.600 --> 35:24.440
Only the ancient divine jade,
the Spirit-Storing Jade,

35:24.520 --> 35:25.840
can hold the Dragon Deity's Power.

35:26.600 --> 35:28.880
The Spirit-Storing Jade
was split in two by heavenly fire.

35:29.480 --> 35:32.920
One became the six-eyed butterfly demon's
Spirit-Storing Butterfly.

35:33.840 --> 35:37.920
The other became the Spirit-Binding Ring
worn by the Dragon Deity.

35:46.320 --> 35:47.080
Wuyi!

35:50.600 --> 35:52.120
So it really was Lu Wuyi.

35:54.640 --> 35:55.760
Return.

36:02.960 --> 36:06.160
The Spirit-Binding Ring
refused my summons.

36:07.280 --> 36:08.200
How is that possible?

36:09.560 --> 36:13.440
The ring has accepted Lu Wuyi
as its master.

36:30.960 --> 36:32.880
Where could she have taken Long?

36:35.160 --> 36:37.240
What Lu Wuyi wants has always been
the Dragon Deity's Power.

36:37.320 --> 36:38.600
Han Ba said…

36:38.680 --> 36:40.480
I hid the Dragon Deity's Power

36:41.840 --> 36:43.480
in the place where I first met Su Jian.

36:47.800 --> 36:49.080
The Wei mansion's weaving workshop.

36:57.760 --> 37:00.320
I… I want to go home.

37:01.760 --> 37:02.800
Don't be afraid.

37:06.160 --> 37:07.720
You'll be home soon.

37:09.840 --> 37:10.920
The Wei mansion?

37:11.000 --> 37:12.080
Isn't that just an ordinary household?

37:12.160 --> 37:13.720
How could it possibly hide
the Dragon Deity's Power?

37:14.320 --> 37:17.920
The giant axle in the workshop
is the core of a Firefluff Tree.

37:18.000 --> 37:20.280
I noticed it the first time
I went to the Wei mansion.

37:20.360 --> 37:21.480
Back then, I wondered

37:21.560 --> 37:24.200
why Xiaowei always fled
to the weaving workshop

37:24.280 --> 37:25.840
<i>to escape the Ice Curse.</i>

37:28.320 --> 37:30.000
The Firefluff Tree is of fire.

37:30.080 --> 37:31.440
The Ice Curse can't get close to it.

37:32.920 --> 37:35.120
Han Ba hid the Dragon Deity's Power
inside the tree core

37:35.200 --> 37:37.680
and cultivated there to keep
his demonic energy from leaking.

37:38.680 --> 37:40.120
What's a Firefluff Tree?

37:40.200 --> 37:41.800
It sounds pretty incredible.

37:41.880 --> 37:44.400
In remote antiquity,
heaven and earth split apart.

37:44.480 --> 37:46.440
Nuwa sought five-colored stones
to mend the sky

37:46.520 --> 37:48.320
and sent the Fox Queen to keep the earth
together with four pillars of ice.

37:48.400 --> 37:50.320
Where the Four Ice Pillars stood

37:50.400 --> 37:52.960
grew four divine trees
of metal, earth, water, and fire.

37:53.040 --> 37:55.600
The Firefluff Tree was one of them.

37:58.040 --> 38:01.360
Han Ba said that as soon
as Mu Long woke up,

38:02.680 --> 38:04.000
the seal would undo itself.

38:05.440 --> 38:08.040
Oh, no. Let's go!

38:20.640 --> 38:22.280
Wake up.

38:30.520 --> 38:31.600
Wuyi,

38:33.000 --> 38:34.560
where… where am I?

38:35.080 --> 38:36.320
Where's Mr. Yan?

39:02.360 --> 39:03.320
Kneel.

39:51.240 --> 39:52.400
Drink it.

40:04.360 --> 40:05.680
I know him!

40:05.760 --> 40:07.280
I've seen him at the Dragon Deity Temple!

40:07.360 --> 40:09.000
He's Master Chi Wen!

40:09.080 --> 40:11.040
The Dragon Deity has answered our prayers!

40:11.120 --> 40:12.800
We're saved!

40:12.880 --> 40:14.840
-Master Chi Wen!
-Master Chi Wen,

40:14.920 --> 40:17.800
-please send us rain!
-Master Chi Wen, save us!

40:17.880 --> 40:19.680
You can't just stand by and watch us die!

40:19.760 --> 40:21.520
Master Chi Wen!

40:21.600 --> 40:23.160
Master Chi Wen!

40:24.040 --> 40:25.160
He's not the Dragon Deity.

40:25.240 --> 40:26.560
-He can't help us!
-Master Chi Wen…

40:26.640 --> 40:28.240
‎-Master Chi Wen…
‎-You did nothing!

40:29.120 --> 40:31.520
-He's not the Dragon Deity!
-He's a fake!

40:31.600 --> 40:33.200
He's a fraud!

40:33.280 --> 40:34.960
You're a fraud!

40:35.040 --> 40:36.920
<i>Why did you lie to us?</i>

40:43.960 --> 40:45.720
Why?

40:48.920 --> 40:51.280
Why can't I change the ending

40:52.280 --> 40:54.760
after everything I've done?

41:06.400 --> 41:07.440
Why?

41:54.760 --> 41:56.080
<i>Why?</i>

41:57.120 --> 41:58.360
<i>Why?</i>

42:11.600 --> 42:14.280
<i>Ji Ling. Ji Ling.</i>

42:15.200 --> 42:16.400
<i>Ji Ling, wake up.</i>

42:18.440 --> 42:19.560
<i>Ji Ling.</i>
